Package com.bonitasoft.engine.api

Interface ProfileAPI

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ProfileAPI
    public interface ProfileAPI
extends ProfileAPI
    Profiles are a notion used in Bonita Portal to give and control access to some specific features of the Bonita suite. Profiles are associated to Bonita Identity / Organization notions: users, groups, roles, memberships. ProfileAPI gives FULL access on profile administration: creation / update / removal of profiles, adding / removing members to / from a profile, retrieving / searching for profiles.
    Import / export of all profiles is also part of this API.
    Author:
    Celine Souchet, Matthieu Chaffotte
